Focus on testing the changes made in Phases 1-4:

Phase 1 - Critical Infrastructure:
- Verify NO Embedly iframes exist (should use direct Vimeo embeds)
- Verify video player elements exist on index.html, about-us.html, crypto-education.html
- Verify news sections have real content (no "Text Link" or "Binance Twitter" placeholders)
- Verify all external links have target="_blank" and rel="noopener"

Phase 2 - Content Integrity:
- Verify Mission and Vision sections have distinct SVG icons
- Verify EBooks "Browse EBooks" button links to #ebooks-collection
- Verify platform links have real URLs

Phase 3 - Brand Consistency:
- Verify NO instances of "Count Wise" or "Count Wize" (should be "CountWize")
- Verify NO em-dashes in headlines

Phase 4 - Layout Polish:
- Verify .core-values-heading-wrapper uses flex-direction: column
- Verify .blog-insights-wrapper uses flexbox with justify-content: center
- Verify hero button is not absolutely positioned off-screen
